title: Parachute demonstration at Nationals game triggers false alarm evacuation at US Capitol - CNN
content:
1. Parachute demonstration at Nationals game triggers false alarm evacuation at US Capitol  CNN
  2. Parachute demo at Nationals Park causes Capitol evacuation  CBS New York
  3. Capitol Police give all clear after issuing evacuation order amid 'probable threat' of 'aircraft intrusion'  Fox News
  4. U.S. Capitol evacuated due to parachute demo error at D-backs, Nationals game  12 News
  5. Capitol Police backtrack on airplane threat after ordering evacuation  POLITICO
  6. View Full Coverage on Google News
description: A military parachute event featuring the Army Golden Knights at Washington's Nationals Park Wednesday night inadvertently triggered a "probable threat" warning at the US Capitol and prompted an evacuation order, sources familiar with the matter tell CNN.
